{"lemma":"ضارِبَةٍ","slug":"ضارِبَةٍ","root":"ض.ر.ب","root_slug":"ض-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25690"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fight"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to speculate, to venture"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of ضَرَبَ (ḍaraba)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/dˤaː.ra.ba/","/dˤaː.rib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25690","headword_ar":"ضاربهُ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaArabapN","text_ar":"مُضَارَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAbN","text_ar":"ضَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He contended with him in beating, striking, smiting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hitting; he beat him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being beaten,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he returned him beating for beating, blow for blow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blows for blows; he bandied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exchanged, blows with him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he contended with him in fight."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) One says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DArbhu faDarabahu","text_ar":"ضاربهُ فَضَرَبَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. of the latter verb"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) agreeably with the general rule respecting verbs signifying the surpassing, or overcoming, in a contest, (MF, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He contended with him in beating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and he surpassed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcame him, therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) See also 6. ―         -b2-  [Golius says, as on the authority of the KL, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DArb","text_ar":"ضارب"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Coivit"},{"kind":"text","text":"camelus; ” and Freytag, as on the authority of the K, that it signifies “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inivit"},{"kind":"text","text":"camelus camelam: ” but in the KL it is only said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAbN","text_ar":"ضَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. of a verb having this meaning; and its verb in this sense, as is said in the S and A and Msb and K, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which has been thus expl. in the first paragraph.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DArb fiY AlmaAli","text_ar":"ضارب فِى المَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlmaAli","text_ar":"بِالمَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaArabapN","text_ar":"مُضَارَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He trafficked with the property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DArb lahu","text_ar":"ضارب لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY maAlihi","text_ar":"فِى مَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DArbhu fY AlmaAli","text_ar":"ضاربهُ فى المَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n. as above, (S, A, Mgh,) means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He trafficked for him with his property"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (A, Mgh;) because he who does so generally journeys in the land seeking gain; (Mgh;) app. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~arobu fiY","text_ar":"الضَّرْبُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the journeying in the land] for the purpose of seeking sustenance: (TA:) and is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAraDahu","text_ar":"قَارَضَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Mgh, K, * TA, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gave him of his property for the purpose of his trafficking therewith on the condition that the gain should be between them two"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that the latter should have a certain share of the gain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and accord. to En-Nadr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DArbhu","text_ar":"ضاربهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of him who does thus and also of the person thus employed. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","MF"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}